					<h1>Documentation</h1>
					<hr />
					<p>
						Lander8 is a scalable analytics tool built for businesses. We make it easy to measure and stay on top of your business' analytics and 
						provide a solution that is easy to integrate while still being relatively powerful. Here's how you can get started:
					</p>
